To play my Tic-Tac-Toe game, follow the following steps:

1. Run the game through tic/Main.java
2. Click the "Start New Game" button to start a new game of Tic-Tac-Toe
3. On X's turn, click on an empty board slot to place an X.
   On O's turn, click on an empty board slot to place an O.
4. Repeat step 3 to play Tic-Tac-Toe.
5. At any point in step 4, press 'r' to open the menu screen, pausing the game. You can start a new game from here with the button.
6. After the game is complete, press 'r' and click the button to start a new game.
7. Resize the window if desired!
